List images embedded in a document (filter, dimensions, bits-per-component, byte size). With `--extract`, dump each image to disk using the native format's file extension

Usage: udoc images [OPTIONS] <FILE>

Arguments:
  <FILE>  Input document

Options:
  -o, --output <FILE>    Write the listing here instead of stdout
      --format <FORMAT>  Listing format: `json` (default) or `text` [default: json]
      --extract <DIR>    Dump each image to this directory
  -h, --help             Print help
